      >
        <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl">
          <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-normal text-[#3B3B3B] md:text-3xl">
            Our community provides ways for people of all ages and interests to
            effect real change.
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-10 max-w-3xl text-lg text-neutral-600">
            Select a pathway below to learn more about how you can get involved.
          </p>

